<div class="elementor-widget-container">
<div class="elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix">
<p>Our history brings so many controversies into todays society, and by forming peaceful petitions and movements, we want to get rid of multiple ancient horrible issues:</p><ul class="trx_addons_list_dot"><li>Ethic discrimination in any type of demonstration.</li><li>Police violence and black citizens&#8217; murders.</li><li>Improvement of the criminal justice system &amp; prosecutors.</li></ul><p>We need to show our support to those whose families have faced with racism, healthcare denial during COVID-19, violence, social, political and economic inequality. We are asking you to participate in our movement for human rights in 2020!</p> </div>
